// Generated by Cypress Author — 2026-05-28
// Covers: Race Log page UI — /main/running/race-log and /main/running/race-log/:id
//
// States tested:
//   - loading: skeleton (visible while fetch is in-flight)
//   - error: error container with "Try again" retry button
//   - empty: Medal icon + "No races logged yet" + CTA button
//   - list: renders race table rows ordered by race_date DESC (each row navigates to detail on click)
//
// Race table row:
//   - title, DNF badge, distance label (type column), date, dist, time, pace, place (#), male (#)
//   - clicking a row navigates to /main/running/race-log/:id
//   - no inline edit/delete buttons on list rows
//
// Add modal (RaceFormModal):
//   - id="raceLogFormModal" on DialogContent
//   - id="raceDate" on calendar popover trigger Button (NOT an input — use .click() + gridcell)
//   - id="dnf" on DNF Checkbox (Radix: <button role="checkbox">)
//   - id="finishTime" on finish time Input
//   - after successful save: modal closes and router navigates to new entry's detail page
//
// Edit modal (EditRaceModal — detail page only):
//   - only accessible from /main/running/race-log/:id
//   - edit button (id="editRaceBtn_raceDetailPage") is inside ActivitySection which only renders
//     when activity data is loaded; stub activity fetch to reveal the button
//   - id="editRaceModal_raceDetailPage" on DialogContent
//   - id="editRaceSaveBtn_raceDetailPage" on save button
//   - title input id="editRaceTitle" (NOT raceTitle)
//
// Delete confirmation (detail page only):
//   - id="deleteRaceBtn_raceDetailPage" on delete button
//   - id="deleteRaceConfirmBtn_raceDetailPage" on confirm button in AlertDialog

